(6, 'about_index', '{\"pic\":[\"201902\\/5c74f06c04e20.jpg\"],\"qy_upload\":\"\",\"content_en\":\"&lt;article&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: inherit; text-rendering: geometricprecision; margin: 1rem 0px 30px; padding: 0px; border: 0px none; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: 300; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.2; font-family: &amp;quot;songti SC&amp;quot;, SimSun, STSong, Times, &amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;, serif; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh&amp;nbsp;is a brand of high quality and lifestyle resort hotel. It was founded by Duan Qiang, chairman of the World Tourism Alliance, China Tourism Association and the Shoulv&amp;nbsp;Travel Group.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Duan Qiang, chairman of the board of directors, put forward the development ideas of &amp;quot;taking the international road, creating national brand&amp;quot; and &amp;quot;serving China&amp;quot;. Mr. Adrian Zecha said that the idea of creating Ahnluh&amp;nbsp;was put forward to him by Chairman Duan Qiang, and it fits in with each other.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh&amp;nbsp;is located in portal cities and natural and cultural resorts, dedicated to serving people (groups) who yearn for a better life and providing opportunities for those who are interested in the cultural travel industry.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: aria