(8, 'index_about', '{\"pic\":\"201902\\/5c74efe317ed0.jpg\",\"qy_upload\":\"\",\"content_en\":\"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh is located on the Bank of Qiandao lake, which has 1078 islands. It is known as &amp;quot;the first beautiful water in the world&amp;quot;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px;&quot;&gt;It inherits the artistic conception of Mr. Wu Guanzhong&amp;#39;s &amp;quot;ink painted Jiangnan&amp;quot;. The Hui architecture complex of Ming and Qing Dynasties contains modern and simple elements, which is also suitable for the past and the present.&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px;&quot;&gt;There are 84 Villas, a full-time restaurant with local characteristics, a Chinese restaurant, an indoor and outdoor infinite swimming pool, a Taiji Hall, a spa and conference facilities in Ahnluh Qiandao lake.&lt;\\/p&gt;\",\"content\":\"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: proxima-nova, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.07px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u5b89\\u9e93\\u5750\\u843d\\u5728\\u62e5\\u6709 1078 \\u4e2a\\u5c9b\\u5c7f\\uff0c\\u88ab\\u8a89\\u4e3a \\u201c\\u5929\\u4e0b\\u7b2c\\u4e00\\u79c0\\u6c34\\u201d \\u7684\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u5317\\u5cb8\\u3002&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: proxima-nova, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.07px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;\\u627f\\u88ad\\u4e8e\\u5434\\u51a0\\u4e2d\\u5148\\u751f\\u201c\\u6c34\\u58a8\\u6c5f\\u5357\\u201d\\u7684\\u610f\\u5883\\uff0c\\u660e\\u6e05\\u5fbd\\u6d3e\\u5efa\\u7b51\\u7fa4\