(18, 'about_about', '{\"pic\":[\"201902\\/5c74f16bb90f0.jpg\"],\"qy_upload\":\"\",\"content_en\":\"&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh Qiandao Lake&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br\\/&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Exploring and understanding the spirit of Chinese traditional culture, among them, Mr. Wu Guanzhong&amp;#39;s large blanks of Chinese ink painting in the south of the Yangtze River and the seemingly random expression of Chinese artistic conception presented by several lines of ink have inspired us. Ahnluh&amp;nbsp;Qiandao Lake is mainly to create an abstract Chinese artistic conception, rather than pursuing too much &amp;quot;imitation of ancient realism&amp;quot; to build it into a painting in the south of the Yangtze River in the real world.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ahnluh Qiandao Lake is located in the hinterland of Qiandaohu Scenic Area, extending to the two peninsulas on the lake, with birds singing in the mountains. The overall style of the hotel is white walls and black tiles. The long and short black sloping roofs end with black curved eaves. Against the white walls, they are like the black lines in Chinese ink and wash paintings. The large glass on the facade of the building and the black window wall make the whole building very modern. In the shade of green trees, buildings stand in black and white, facing the lake, a vast water village.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;The public area of the hotel consists of the arrival lobby, the main building of the public area, the cigar bar of the academy and SPA.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;At the beginning of entering the hotel area, we first designed and planted a forest, crossing the forest, suddenly a pool, white walls and black tiles arrived at the lobby, together with the reflection in the water, and finally jumped into sight. After the fatigue of the boat and car, the atmosphere of arrival is created, which makes the guests feel calm and relaxed in the process of entering. Entering the gate, the visitors are presented with the waterscape of the inner courtyard. At the end of the corridor along the central axis, the main building of the lobby stands as if it were cordial and solemn. Entering the lobby, the whole floor glass along the lake presents the beautiful scenery of Qiandao Lake in front of the guests for the first time. This kind of careful design pays attention to details, hoping to give the guests a sense of first arrival experience.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;As the main building of the public area, it is situated in the middle of the two peninsulas. The building is two stories and stands near the lake. Entering through the Chinese Moon Cave Gate, the visitors will first see a delicate, concise and Zen-like atrium, with 140 people on both sides of the atrium and four 10-person private rooms along the lake. Unlike other hotels, there are many restaurants. The hotel only has one main restaurant, which is also the Chinese upper class targeted by the brand. The atrium is carefully arranged to simplify and refine. The embodiment of elegant lifestyle. On the second floor of the main building, there are three meeting rooms, which can be used as a multi-functional hall after opening the connection, and another half-outdoor activity space. There are boundless pools outside the conference room and semi-outdoor activity space, with a view of Qiandao Lake.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br\\/&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\",\"content\":\"&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \\u5b8b\\u4f53, SimSun; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;\\u5343 \\u5c9b \\u6e56 \\u5b89 \\u9e93&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;br\\/&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \\u5b8b\\u4f53, SimSun; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\\u63a2\\u7d22\\u4e86\\u89e3\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u4f20\\u7edf\\u6587\\u5316\\u7cbe\\u795e\\uff0c\\u5176\\u4e2d\\uff0c\\u5434\\u51a0\\u4e2d\\u5148\\u751f\\u7684\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u6c5f\\u5357\\u6c34\\u58a8\\u753b\\u5927\\u7247\\u7559\\u767d\\uff0c\\u770b\\u4f3c\\u968f\\u610f\\u7684\\u51e0\\u7b14\\u58a8\\u7ebf\\u52fe\\u52d2\\u6240\\u5448\\u73b0\\u7684\\u6781\\u5177\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u610f\\u5883\\u7684\\u8868\\u8fbe\\uff0c\\u7ed9\\u4e88\\u4e86\\u542f\\u53d1\\u2014\\u2014\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u5b89\\u9e93\\uff0c\\u4ee5\\u8425\\u9020\\u62bd\\u8c61\\u7684\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u610f\\u5883\\u4e3a\\u4e3b\\uff0c\\u800c\\u975e\\u8ffd\\u6c42\\u8fc7\\u591a\\u7684\\u201c\\u4eff\\u53e4\\u5199\\u5b9e\\u201d\\uff0c\\u5c06\\u5176\\u5efa\\u6210\\u771f\\u5b9e\\u4e16\\u754c\\u4e2d\\u7684\\u4e00\\u5e45\\u6c5f\\u5357\\u6c34\\u58a8\\u5199\\u610f\\u753b\\u5377\\u3002&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \\u5b8b\\u4f53, SimSun; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u5b89\\u9e93\\u9152\\u5e97\\u5730\\u5904\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u666f\\u533a\\u8179\\u5730\\u5ef6\\u4f38\\u5411\\u6e56\\u9762\\u7684\\u4e24\\u4e2a\\u534a\\u5c9b\\u4e0a\\uff0c\\u9e1f\\u9e23\\u5c71\\u5e7d\\u3002\\u9152\\u5e97\\u6574\\u4f53\\u98ce\\u683c\\u4e3a\\u767d\\u5899\\u9ed1\\u74e6\\uff0c\\u9ed1\\u8272\\u7684\\u957f\\u77ed\\u53cc\\u5761\\u5c4b\\u9762\\u4ee5\\u9ed1\\u8272\\u5f27\\u5f62\\u5c01\\u6a90\\u677f\\u6536\\u5934\\uff0c\\u5728\\u767d\\u5899\\u7684\\u6620\\u886c\\u4e4b\\u4e0b\\uff0c\\u5b9b\\u82e5\\u4e2d\\u56fd\\u6c34\\u58a8\\u753b\\u4e2d\\u5199\\u6