(22, 'Product_index', '{\"pic\":[\"201903\\/5c7dd8704d936.jpg\"],\"qy_upload\":\"\",\"description\":\"\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u5b89\\u9e93\\u5730\\u5904\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u897f\\u5357\\u6e56\\u533a\\uff0c\\u5750\\u843d\\u4e8e\\u5343\\u5e74\\u72ee\\u57ce\\u59dc\\u5bb6\\u9547\\uff0c\\u5468\\u8fb9\\u6709\\u590d\\u539f1400\\u5e74\\u65b0\\u5b89\\u6587\\u5316\\u7684\\u6587\\u6e0a\\u72ee\\u57ce\\uff0c\\u6df3\\u6734\\u7f8e\\u4e3d\\u7684\\u82b9\\u5ddd\\u53e4\\u6751\\uff0c\\u5343\\u5c9b\\u6e56\\u552f\\u4e00\\u7684\\u6e56\\u6cca\\u578b\\u6e7f\\u5730\\u9f99\\u5ddd\\u6e7e\\u6e7f\\u5730\\uff0c\\u611f\\u53d7\\u53e4\\u6587\\u5316\\u548c\\u81ea\\u7136\\u7684\\u6709\\u8da3\\u7ed3\\u5408\\u3002\",\"description_en\":\"Ahnluh Qiandao Lake is located in the southwest Lake area of Qiandao Lake. It is located in Jiangjia Town, the Millennium Lion City. It is surrounded by Wenyuan Lion City, the ancient village of Qianchuan, the only Lake Wetland of Qiandao Lake, Longchuan Bay wetland, which has restored the culture of Xin\'an in 1400 years, and enjoys the interesting combination of ancient culture and nature.\",\"pic1\":[\"201903\\/5c7dd9b4be4a4.jpg\"],\"pic2\":[\"201903\\/5c7f7bc91979c.jpg\",\"201903\\/5c7f7bcfd28d4.jpg\",\"201903\\/5c7f7bd317e68.jpg\"],\"content_en\":\"&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;1584&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Wenyuan Lion City&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(2 km from the hotel, about 5 minutes by car, 10 minutes by foot).&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;It only takes about 10 minutes to walk to Wenyuan Lion City starting from the hotel.On both sides are the acient style buildings and shops, as well as the exquisitely carved and well-preserved ancient archways, which not only duplicate the underwater ancient city ashore, you can also enjoy the Xin&amp;#39;an culture 1400 years ago again!&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br\\/&gt;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;\\/td&gt;&lt;\\/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;1584&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Qianchuan ancient village&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;(about 10 kilometers away from the hotel, about 15 minutes by car).&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Not far from the hotel, there is also an ancient village, Qinchuan Village, which has a 750-year history deep in Qiandao Lake. Compared with Wuzhen and Xitang, it has a more flavor of Jiangnan, without too much noise and no commercial atmosphere. A small stream travels quietly through the town. Old Huizhou buildings with white walls and black tiles can be seen everywhere.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;\\/td&gt;&lt;\\/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;1584&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Longchuan Bay Wetland Scenic Area, International Fishing Center&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;(about 7 kilometers from the hotel, about 12 minutes by car).&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Longchuan Bay Scenic Area of Qiandao Lake, The whole scenic area is surrounded by scattered islands and twists and turns of harbor branches. It forms the Longchuan scenic spot of &amp;quot;islands in lakes and lakes in islands&amp;quot;, which is the only Lake Wetland in Qiandao Lake. The International Fishing Center has an area of 2,000 mu. It is the first large-scale fishing &amp;quot;special zone&amp;quot; allowed by Chun&amp;#39;an County&amp;#39;s policy.&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;\\/td&gt;&lt;\\/tr&gt;&lt;\\/tbody&gt;&lt;\\/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;\",\"content\":\"&lt;table&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td width=&quot;1584&quot; valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: \\u5b8b\\u4f53, SimSun; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\\u6587\\u6e0a\\u72ee\\u57ce\\uff08\\u8ddd\\u79bb\\u9152\\u5e972\\u516c\\u91cc\\uff0c\\u8f66\\u7a0b\\u7ea65\\u5206\\u949f\\uff0c\\u6b65\\u884c10\\u5206\\u949f\\u3002\\uff09&lt;\\/span&gt;&lt;br\\/&gt;&lt;\\/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;