(28, '私人订制', 'Personal Dining Tailor', '私人订制', 'Personal Dining tailor', '需提前3天预定', 'Three days in advance', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '我们为您私人订制别具一格的难忘主题餐饮体验。不论是为爱人打造纪念日的浪漫柔情，或是以一场美味野餐策划一次生日惊喜，还是来一场回味无穷的烛光晚餐。', 'We customize a unique and unforgettable theme catering experience for you. Whether it\'s a romantic anniversary for your lover, a birthday surprise with a delicious picnic, or a candlelit dinner with endless aftertaste.', '201903/5c7e19b81fd36.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1551283200),
(29, '茶寮', 'Tea House', '中式茗茶', 'Chinese Tea', '11:00-19:00', '11:00-19:00', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '来杭州当然要品好茶，千岛湖安麓茶寮为您准备了多款上好的茶，在青山绿水环抱中品味茶香，享受好茶，好景，好时光。\r\n\r\n凝神静气，深入中国传统茶文化的世界。潜心学习中国茶艺从冲泡、闻香到品茗的各个步骤，体悟以茶会友的和谐境界。品一杯清香四溢的杭白菊茶，清心明目，驱热解暑；或体验一场静心宁神的私人茶事，在淡淡茶香余韵中与家人共赏多款精选茶饮，感受简单细腻的生活美学。\r\n\r\n                                                        ', 'Of course, to Hangzhou, we should have good tea. The Tea House of Ahn Luh Qiandao Lake has prepared many kinds of good tea for you. We can enjoy tea fragrance, good tea, good scenery and good time surrounded by green mountains and waters.\r\nDeepen into the world of traditional Chinese tea culture by concentrating on tranquility. Concentrate on learning all steps of Chinese tea art from brewing, smelling fragrance to tea tasting, and realize the harmonious realm of meeting friends with tea. Taste a cup of Hangzhou white chrysanthemum tea with delicate fragrance, clear heart and clear eyes, drive away heat and relieve heat; or experience a quiet and quiet private tea affair, enjoy a variety of selected tea drinks with family in the fragrance of light tea, feel simple and delicate life aesthetics. The Tea House is open from 11:00 a.m. to 19:00 p.m.\r\n\r\n\r\n                                                        ', '201903/5c7e19c4ed397.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1550678400),
(30, '望湖/美食廊', 'The Lake / Gourmet Gallery', '下午茶/中西式小食/雪茄/威士忌', 'Afternoon tea/Tapas/cigars/whiskey', '10:00-22:00', '10:00-22:00', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '望湖美食廊不同于传统意义上的酒吧，其独有的空间分布及多功能性的布局、令您像置身于自家的起居室及会客厅。宾客可在这里享用丰富精致的轻奢美点与小食，上好年份的威士忌，精选古巴雪茄，亦或是精心调制的鸡尾酒。餐厅从上午10:00营业至晚间22:00。白天，投射自不同角度的阳光阴影变幻在空间里留下别具意趣的影像。是您放松身心与珍享时光的好去处。', 'The Lake gourmet Gallery is different from the traditional bar. Its unique spatial distribution and multi-functional layout make you feel like you are in your living room and meeting room. Guests can enjoy rich and delicate light and luxurious snacks, good-year whiskey, selected Cuban cigars, or elaborate cocktails. The dining room can accommodate 72 guests.\r\nThe Lake gourmet Gallery is different from the traditional bar. Its unique spatial distribution and multi-functional layout make you feel like you are in your living room and meeting room. Guests can enjoy rich and delicate light and luxurious snacks, good-year whiskey, selected Cuban cigars, or elaborate cocktails. The Gallery is open from 10 a.m. to 2200 p.m. During the day, sunshine and shadows projected from different angles leave interesting images in space. It\'s a good place for you to relax and enjoy your time. \r\n', '201903/5c7e199677f6b.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1551283200),
(31, 'PDR/私宴包厢', 'Personal Dining Room', '中国/本地风味', 'Chinese/Typical Flavor', '11:00-14:30      17:00-22:00', '11:00-14:30      17:00-22:00', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '在千岛湖安麓私宴包厢用餐一如在家飨宴待客般自在。\r\n传统的中式/本土菜肴皆取材于当地，并遵照本土及厨师团队以匠心演绎为您呈现精炼后的本土美味。餐厅提供四间私人包厢，每间包厢均可容纳12位宾客，可满足诸如家庭聚会或小型庆典等活动的需求。', 'Experience the customs of a traditional Chinese restaurant combined with the familiarity reserved for guests welcomed into your own home. The PDR also has Four private dining rooms that can each seat 12 guests.\r\n\r\nThis is the convivial setting for exquisite dining that celebrates seasonal ingredients, sourced locally and prepared in Zhejiang or Hangzhou Flavored. For special occasions and family gatherings, the restaurant also has Four private dining rooms that can each seat 12 guests, overlooking breathtaking views and where the food is cooked in front of you by your own personal chef.', '201903/5c7e19885d5de.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1551283200),
(32, '湖景/全日餐厅', 'Lake View/All Day Dining', '中国/本地/国际风味', 'Chinese/Typical/ International Flavor', '07:00-23:00', '07:00-23:00', '', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '', '作为千岛湖安麓餐饮的根本，客人可以在湖景中品味本土厨师团队匠心演绎的三餐膳食。\r\n千岛湖的环境得天独厚，既有优质的水产资源，又有丰富的草本蔬果。通过对当地食材、风土与文化重新整合，回到食物的本味和原点，诠释具有当地特色的岁时料理。中国饮食文化博大精深，我们要做的就是把地道、时令和有温度的美食呈现给大家，一起体验每一餐的温暖、满足和惊喜。\r\n餐厅可容纳166位宾客，重新诠释的新中式用餐氛围，用时尚潮流的感触表达本地口味，以及岁时料理的烹饪理念，为客人创造别具一格的用餐体验。\r\n', 'As the basis of Restaurant in Ahn Luh Qiandao Lake, guests can enjoy the three meals elaborated by the local chef team in the lake view. \r\nThe environment of Qiandao Lake is unique. It has not only high quality aquatic resources, but also abundant herbs, vegetables and fruits. Through the re-integration of local food materials, customs and culture, we can return to the original flavor and point of food and interpret the age cuisine with local characteristics. Chinese food culture is extensive and profound. What we need to do is to present authentic, seasonal and temperate food to you, and experience the warmth, satisfaction and surprise of each meal together. The dining room can accommodate 166 guests. \r\nThe restaurant is open from 07:00 a.m. to 23:00 p.m. and offers Chinese/local specialties and international delicacies. Re-interpret the new Chinese dining atmosphere, express local taste with the feeling of fashion trend, as well as the cooking concept of age cooking, to create a unique dining experience for guests. \r\n', '201903/5c7e197a8f112.jpg', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 1551283200);

